        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 1 at 3:15PM PDT by NWS Pendleton OR</headline>
        <description>At 315 PM PDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Camp Sherman, or 28 miles northwest of Redmond, moving northwest at
10 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Camp Sherman.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
